             was indicted for <rs id="t17851214-89-off412" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17851214-89-off412" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17851214-89-off412" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously and feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17851214-89-victim833" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Clarke
                        <interp inst="t17851214-89-victim833" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
